 or punish a Muslim man, then turn it into purification and mercy for him.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6361, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2601 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":681,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/04\/07\/mercy-to-the-worlds\/","url_meta":{"origin":10925,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Mercy: The Prophet is sent as mercy to the worlds","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 7, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: It was said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, pray against the idolaters!\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, I was not sent to invoke curses, but rather I was only sent as mercy.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2599 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":23932,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/10\/27\/umar-ii-curses-becomes-worse\/","url_meta":{"origin":10925,"position":2},"title":"Umar II on Curses: He curses his oppressor until he is even worse","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 27, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Ribah ibn 'Ubaydah reported: I was sitting with Umar ibn Abdul Aziz, may Allah have mercy on him, when the ruler Al-Hajjaj was mentioned, so I reviled and denounced him. Umar said, \u201cCalm down, O Ribah! Verily, I have heard that a man might be oppressed with a great wrong,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6580,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/17\/muhammad-prophet-tawbah-rahmah\/","url_meta":{"origin":10925,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Muhammad: Prophet of repentance, Prophet of mercy","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 17, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"\u201cI am Muhammad; I am Ahmad; I am the ender of Prophethood; I am the gatherer on the Day of Resurrection; I am the Prophet of repentance; and I am the Prophet of mercy.\u201d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0627 \u0645\u064f\u062d\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0651\u062f\u064c \u0648\u064e\u0623\u064e\u062d\u0652\u0645\u064e\u062f\u064f \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064f\u0642\u064e\u0641\u0650\u0651\u064a \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0627\u0634\u0650\u0631\u064f \u0648\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u064f\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u062a\u064e\u0651\u0648\u0652\u0628\u064e\u0629\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u064f\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u064e\u0651\u062d\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0629\u0650","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41343,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/10\/04\/not-sent-to-curse\/","url_meta":{"origin":10925,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Cursing: The Prophet not sent to invoke curses","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 4, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":